-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Steps For Installing 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. download source from https://github.com/freeEdu/freeEdu [Place @ /var/www]
2. download sql from http://is.gd/freeedu_sql 
3. download these files 
	3.1 constants.php from http://is.gd/freeedu_constants
	3.2 connection.php from http://is.gd/freeedu_connection
4. place constants.php in freeEdu/misc [Create folder misc before that]
5. place connection.php in lib/
6. edit misc/constants.php [$dbuname,$dbpass]
7. edit connection.php also in the same way
8. Bingo You Are Done! hit localhost/freeEdu .. 
9. Hit the help icon for login! 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
